  "section_name": "Financial Analysis",
  "text": "Cash flow quality remains exceptional, with Q3 2025 operating cash flow of $27,867,000,000 and free cash flow of $24,405,000,000. The free cash flow margin of 25.95% indicates strong conversion of revenue into distributable cash. Capital expenditure for the quarter was $3,462,000,000, reflecting disciplined investment in infrastructure while maintaining substantial cash generation. This cash flow profile supports continued capital return programs, with $21,075,000,000 in stock buybacks executed during Q3.",
